Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.09,0:00:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说矢野和大他两岁的女生交往
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.20,0:00:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他喜欢年纪大的么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.20,0:00:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 交往了多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是从矢野初二末到初三的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.74,0:00:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,444)\fs22}才半年 好短暂呐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.72,0:00:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,444)\fs22}哎 不长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.75,0:00:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消息不知道是谁传出来的 大家都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.38,0:00:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在混乱着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.18,0:00:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.56,0:00:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以上体育课了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.64,0:00:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我这次数学考了34分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 终于脱离红灯了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.34,0:00:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那下次你必须得56分以上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平均分不到30分的话 一样会留级吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.29,0:00:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.23,0:00:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.09,0:00:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 和平时没什么两样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.15,0:01:03.05,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}嘘つきなあなた 泣き虫のあたし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.10,0:01:08.95,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どうして？ うまくいかないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:14.92,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}オシャレした髪も ラインストーンの爪も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.18,0:01:20.82,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたは気付きもしないね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.12,0:01:27.95,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}LOVE 悲しい涙なんかじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.39,0:01:32.95,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}目が乾いてヒリヒリするだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.20,0:01:35.91,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}転んでばっかり I LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.03,0:01:47.45,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君だけを あたしだけを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:52.43,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}熱い想いを受け止めて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:59.62,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どこまでも つながってたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.13,0:02:04.45,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}可愛くない泣き顔も
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:06.47,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}全部愛してね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.15,0:01:03.05,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}谎话连篇的你 爱哭鼻子的我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.10,0:01:08.95,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怎么进展得不顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:14.92,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}精心打扮的头发 光彩夺目的指甲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.18,0:01:20.82,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你却都没注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.12,0:01:27.95,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}love 并非悲伤的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.39,0:01:32.95,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}干涩的眼睛只是有些刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.20,0:01:39.21,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪水滚落不停 I love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.03,0:01:47.45,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只有你 只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:52.43,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}理解那炽热的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.01,0:01:59.62,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无论在哪里 都彼此相连
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.13,0:02:04.45,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}连你并不可爱的哭脸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:06.47,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我也深爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧 一点也不像
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,444)\fs22}真的一点也不像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.31,0:02:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旭中的相册
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本同学的姐姐也在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.90,0:02:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 矢野和她交往过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七也来看下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我就 算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 谁能破开五千块
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破不开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 有人能帮我破五千块么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野跟平常一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理所当然吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野一开始就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是我什么都不知道罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.37,0:02:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,444)\fs22}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.12,0:02:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,444)\fs22}拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:02:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委员会延长了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 是几班来着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年五班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只顾着好奇 你生气了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.80,0:03:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没看过那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是想看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.35,0:04:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 我不想在这种情况下看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 我不知道该用什么表情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专挑美女啊 这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.39,0:04:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她 好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可真人比这还漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不行 彻底输了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和山本同学 不太像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁先喜欢上对方的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.24,0:04:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对她一见钟情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后马上就交往了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 花了段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她原来有男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抢过来的么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 讲得那么难听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.31,0:04:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我至今为止从没见过 执着某事的矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:05:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 她是你引以为豪的女朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我第一次真心喜欢上的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然心里很难受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可矢野能笑着和我说这些 我就安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概是 不愿意承认吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.69,0:05:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承认矢野喜欢的人存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.65,0:05:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈 你别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就那么一说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野你喜欢我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.51,0:05:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.11,0:05:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:05:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 绝对有的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.41,0:05:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.37,0:05:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.06,0:06:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 非要问的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.69,0:06:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的不是那种喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在问你是真的真的喜欢我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.03,0:06:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.20,0:06:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要那样的交往
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.47,0:06:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往是因为喜欢才交往的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说“我知道了”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.57,0:06:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我生平第一次告白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么就那么干脆地…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老老实实地说什么“我不知道”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我要是装没听见 嗯一声就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:06:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是睡得很坦然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 不会了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本 你接着做做看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 你看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 你怎么了 脸色不太好哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.18,0:07:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.86,0:07:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对贫血很有效喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.74,0:07:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么温温的 好难喝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.18,0:07:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是午饭剩下来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啊 还没坏的 大概
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.68,0:07:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 又能像平常一样说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.26,0:07:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前问我好几次是真的真的喜欢我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 有那么多次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一遍又一遍地问吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也来问问你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.89,0:08:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的真的喜欢我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答不上来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.34,0:08:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是这种程度而已吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我有点饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃点甜食好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 竹内君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得啊 居然在这看到你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对了 这里是旭中那片儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我们经常在这里聚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 那矢野也在咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.49,0:08:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吧 一块儿坐坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个很好吃哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 能坐进去点儿吗 俩人的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.39,0:08:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们班的班长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那头脑一定很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:08:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 特别是数学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 听说你们和山本有里在一个班
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个超阴暗又让人讨厌的家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.35,0:09:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她姐姐完全不像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.66,0:09:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但不随和还丑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那绝对是因为自卑才显老的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小就一直被人和姐姐比
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.48,0:09:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着那么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就别单凭表面现象说三道四啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.59,0:09:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们初中三年都在一个班
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少比你了解她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 同班了三年就只能讲出这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.07,0:09:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是她好好传话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元晴和奈奈就不会吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是没吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.28,0:09:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那年暑假他们就会在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就不会发生那种…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.04,0:09:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是讲这种事的场合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.19,0:10:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 大家怎么这么严肃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 因为我么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不允许别人说奈奈的坏话喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.48,0:10:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 山本妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.63,0:10:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 她还不错啦 心眼不像外表那么坏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.74,0:10:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥七七
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.61,0:10:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是班会 别摆架子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.38,0:10:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧 白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱包掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:10:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.35,0:11:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是第一次被女人说去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就再多说一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 笨蛋 呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.09,0:11:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妈妈是凸肚脐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你眼里只有奈奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 笨蛋 呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的妈妈不是凸肚脐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的妈妈是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妓女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的女朋友是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.25,0:11:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她和男人在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出车祸的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:11:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和以前的男人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.67,0:12:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们 从来没结束过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.39,0:12:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太认真
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情的真相 我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.61,0:12:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果说我明白一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是哪怕她有一次想见别的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她有那样想法的我也有责任吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道说什么好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.65,0:12:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 短信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问“你们在干吗”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.32,0:12:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在送高桥同学回家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.35,0:13:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不送也可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.07,0:13:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不送也可以 大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去照大头贴好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.85,0:13:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候说这个绝对是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.99,0:13:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不拍全身的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 只拍脸比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.47,0:13:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很久没拍过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细想想 他一直在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.65,0:13:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野啊 你很坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般人很难说出刚才那些话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.78,0:13:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按确定咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 跟变脸似的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.69,0:13:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其怪别人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如怪自己更轻松吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 反了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.21,0:13:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,责怪别人更轻松些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果怪别人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会觉得太不讲理 无法原谅别人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果怪自己 就会觉得这也是没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不生气了 就轻松了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换句话说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很狡猾吧 我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.16,0:14:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按确定咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 一副傻样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,444)\fs22}很笨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么在傻笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我的脸更大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.24,0:14:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像章鱼星人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很可爱呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱吗 章鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.72,0:14:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公交车来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:15:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}校园祭表演节目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前几天的委员会上决定了我们班的表演节目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗憾的是咖啡店的候选班级太多 所以没能通过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.99,0:15:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我们的第三志愿小剧场完美当选了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么第三志愿当选
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥你睡着了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为人家不擅长猜拳嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小剧场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在礼堂而是要借教室演
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了学生评委和老师几乎不会有人来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.37,0:15:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真扫兴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没干劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此为了提高观众数量 我想了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终想出了一个绝佳的点子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演什么还没决定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主角 矢野元晴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.01,0:15:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能招揽客人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.75,0:15:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召集女生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.87,0:15:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 今天要去挑剧本 要哪种呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊 随你的便
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 那么生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总得给你善后吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:15:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善后是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:15:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且 负责服装之类吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真轻松啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 有时候真是挺让人讨厌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.95,0:16:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 情况对自己不利 我就成了讨厌的家伙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs30\pos(580,170)\c&H00e197e5\3a&H00000000&\bord0\fn@方正准圆_GBK\frz-90}上周才告白的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说 是那个事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得那事确实是我有点儿冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是我没眼光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 那就是搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.01,0:16:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs15}说喜欢你{\fs25}那个事 是我搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是都说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.14,0:16:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得 莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.29,0:16:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么搞的我就想找个能杀人的故事 好把主角大卸八块
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.26,0:16:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱情故事不算
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀 了 他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.81,0:17:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七似乎很想杀了矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.24,0:17:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 给你画胡子 胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.72,0:17:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.86,0:17:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天午休时要开委员会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要决定分配教室的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是吗 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.21,0:17:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 什么事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得你们聚一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那都是家常便饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们净是些不积口德的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你们要演戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.84,0:17:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.00,0:17:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说这样可那家伙偏偏…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.77,0:17:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭笨蛋矢野啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.32,0:17:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别提那家伙了 我嘴巴会臭的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你很生气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.52,0:17:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你不觉得那家伙冷血得像是血不流吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.15,0:18:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不把人当人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.96,0:18:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不稍微注意下就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你正好相反啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 折腾了大半天却得不到一点回报
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候看到那种人就上火了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 他能召集大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.82,0:18:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有矢野在 大家都会对演戏感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 有这种人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.97,0:18:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息的时候 他拿起球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.03,0:18:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班上的人就呼一下聚起来被带到操场上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他不在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.02,0:18:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就会觉得好无聊 也就不玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.48,0:18:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种有存在感的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.15,0:18:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 对矢野的这点…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 很憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.14,0:19:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是再说这些傻话 不只是嘴连脑袋都坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.49,0:19:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.36,0:19:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那天起 我们就一直忙着选剧本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没想到两天之后会发生不得了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 没有我们班的教室啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天午休时要开委员会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要决定分配教室的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.00,0:19:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.96,0:19:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说我们班可能没办法演戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 我一点也不为难
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.94,0:19:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥忘开分教室的会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就没给分教室啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.30,0:19:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 也不是没有教室
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:20:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三校舍的话还有空教室
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三校舍太远了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种破校舍谁会去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没干劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎么搞的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是七七的错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是分配教室的人忘记我们班了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七已经努力去抗议过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可他们说已经不能改了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是没参加教室分配会的我们不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坚决不同意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.27,0:20:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥 委员会什么时候开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在完了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还有人留下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.20,0:20:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.99,0:20:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.86,0:20:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事我来负责
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.23,0:20:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.59,0:20:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于教室的分配的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和矢野 不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 都定好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.80,0:21:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,444)\fs22}你们用剩下的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.56,0:21:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,444)\fs22}就是剩下的地方不行 才找你们换的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.97,0:21:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野和别人的想法不同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,444)\fs22}本来是谁组织这事的 让我弄清楚谁负责啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从什么时候有这种感觉的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.32,0:21:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明态度随便 但办事又很认真
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.52,0:21:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明喜欢偷懒 但总能击中要害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一校舍是没办法的了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.87,0:21:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 矢野你这么矛盾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.63,0:21:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是 不帮我善后的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.14,0:22:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我就是容易得意忘形 意志薄弱 八面玲珑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.24,0:22:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徒有责任感 但是靠不住 胆小又心胸狭窄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.72,0:22:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.14,0:22:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烂好人的同义词
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.93,0:22:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没眼光 急匆匆地告白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.33,0:22:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且动不动就依赖别人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.53,0:22:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.45,0:22:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.24,0:22:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.88,0:22:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是在抖包袱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.00,0:22:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒觉得未必那么不好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.19,0:22:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.05,0:22:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烂好人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.60,0:22:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.38,0:22:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告白 也没错得那么离谱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.56,0:22:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.97,0:22:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.31,0:22:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你对重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.63,0:22:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总用“谁知到呢”“不知道啊”打岔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.01,0:22:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没打岔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.39,0:22:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想打马虎的时候我什么都说得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.93,0:23:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都说得出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.53,0:23:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.22,0:23:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.41,0:23:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.85,0:23:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是也有“无法了解的我”吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.79,0:23:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.18,0:23:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 这种事又矛盾了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.80,0:23:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许真的有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.60,0:25:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这就是盲目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.18,0:25:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明没有真心喜欢过别人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.74,0:25:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这才叫做乳臭未干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.77,0:25:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也快谈一次真正的恋爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.47,0:25:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.76,0:25:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野你非常非常喜欢的人可能已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.45,0:25:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可能很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.27,0:25:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我会看着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.88,0:25:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会一直看着矢野你的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.59,0:25:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护着你的
Dialogue: 3,0:21:59.65,0:22:03.98,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ここにいて  いつでも
Dialogue: 3,0:22:05.25,0:22:09.40,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ここにいて　わたしを
Dialogue: 3,0:22:11.20,0:22:15.43,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ここにいて　見ていて
Dialogue: 3,0:22:16.89,0:22:19.51,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}このままずっと
Dialogue: 3,0:22:21.78,0:22:27.33,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}手のひらの中 溢れ出しそうな
Dialogue: 3,0:22:27.82,0:22:32.06,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたがくれた「初めて」
Dialogue: 3,0:22:33.69,0:22:38.89,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}わたし一人じゃ　心が揺れたら
Dialogue: 3,0:22:39.32,0:22:45.55,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}みんなこぼれてしまう
Dialogue: 3,0:22:47.65,0:22:53.05,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたの大きな手で
Dialogue: 3,0:22:53.40,0:22:58.39,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}私ごと掴まえていて
Dialogue: 3,0:22:59.13,0:23:04.57,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}こんなにも　こんなにも
Dialogue: 3,0:23:05.08,0:23:10.31,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}頼りない私のことを
Dialogue: 3,0:23:11.19,0:23:13.55,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}だけど　今は
Dialogue: 3,0:23:14.07,0:23:16.43,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたの手は
Dialogue: 3,0:23:17.59,0:23:20.12,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}少し遠くて
Dialogue: 3,0:23:34.98,0:23:38.96,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ここにいて　やさしく
Dialogue: 3,0:23:40.71,0:23:45.01,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ここにいて　あなたの
Dialogue: 3,0:23:46.60,0:23:50.78,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ここにいて　その手で
Dialogue: 3,0:23:52.33,0:23:55.06,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}包んでいてね
Dialogue: 3,0:23:57.13,0:24:02.78,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつも一人で　歩いてる道は
Dialogue: 3,0:24:03.15,0:24:07.26,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}広すぎて　さみしいだけ
Dialogue: 3,0:24:09.02,0:24:14.31,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}二人で歩けば　幸せな気持ち
Dialogue: 3,0:24:14.68,0:24:21.19,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}それだけでいっぱいよ
Dialogue: 3,0:24:23.15,0:24:28.53,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたが笑颜だったら
Dialogue: 3,0:24:28.82,0:24:34.13,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}私も同じでいたい
Dialogue: 3,0:24:34.53,0:24:40.03,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}それなのに　それなのに
Dialogue: 3,0:24:40.35,0:24:45.90,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}私だけ震えてしまう
Dialogue: 3,0:24:46.50,0:24:48.89,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}風よ　どうか
Dialogue: 3,0:24:49.34,0:24:51.68,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}好きの気持ち
Dialogue: 3,0:24:53.02,0:24:55.91,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そっと伝えて
Dialogue: 3,0:21:59.65,0:22:03.98,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}留在这里吧 无论何时
Dialogue: 3,0:22:05.25,0:22:09.40,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}留在这里吧 在我身边
Dialogue: 3,0:22:11.20,0:22:15.43,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}留在这里吧 注视着我
Dialogue: 3,0:22:16.89,0:22:19.51,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就这样直到永远
Dialogue: 3,0:22:21.78,0:22:27.33,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}似乎要从掌心中溢出的
Dialogue: 3,0:22:27.82,0:22:32.06,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}是你带给我的「最初」
Dialogue: 3,0:22:33.69,0:22:38.89,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我若独自一人 心摇摆不定
Dialogue: 3,0:22:39.32,0:22:45.55,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一切美好就将消散殆尽
Dialogue: 3,0:22:47.65,0:22:53.05,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}用你那双大手
Dialogue: 3,0:22:53.40,0:22:58.39,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}将我抓紧
Dialogue: 3,0:22:59.13,0:23:04.57,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即使是 即使是
Dialogue: 3,0:23:05.08,0:23:10.31,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}将这么冒失的我
Dialogue: 3,0:23:11.19,0:23:13.55,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}但是现在
Dialogue: 3,0:23:14.07,0:23:16.43,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的手
Dialogue: 3,0:23:17.59,0:23:20.12,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}却悄然疏远
Dialogue: 3,0:23:34.98,0:23:38.96,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}留下来吧 饱含温柔
